Regis Aged Care Seeks A$425 Million Five-Year Loan Facility

-- B y   S a r a h   M c D o n a l d
-- 
2011-10-16T23:59:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/regis-aged-care-seeks-a-425-million-five-year-loan-facility.html
 Regis Aged Care Pty. is seeking a
A$425 million five-year loan to refinance existing debt,
according to an e-mailed statement from  Australia & New Zealand
Banking Group Ltd. (ANZ) , which is arranging the facility.  The debt includes two revolving portions totaling A$400
million and a A$25 million working capital facility, according
to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sarah McDonald in Sydney at 
 smcdonald23@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edward Johnson at 
 ejohnson28@bloomberg.net  